## ✨ Core Features

### 1. Intelligent Essay Grading Engine

**What it does:**
- Evaluates student answers based on **meaning and concept mastery**, not keyword matching
- Uses your **golden answer** as the semantic reference for all comparisons
- Grades multiple students simultaneously (up to 10 files in one batch)
- Identifies top performers and struggling students automatically
- Generates specific, actionable feedback for each submission

**Supported Formats:** PDF, DOCX  
**Cost Model:** 1 credit per essay (bulk discounts available)

**Use Case Example:**
> Teacher submits a golden answer for a Chemistry essay on photosynthesis. Twenty student answers are uploaded. Within minutes, Teacher Assistant Agent provides:
> - Individual grades with detailed reasoning
> - Class average and performance distribution
> - In-depth analysis for bottom 3 students
> - Common misconceptions to address in the next lesson
> - **Time saved:** 3.5+ hours of manual grading

---

### 2. Administrative Knowledge Base & RAG

**What it does:**
- Upload school handbooks, curriculum guides, discipline policies, medical protocols
- Ask natural language questions: *"What's our absence policy?"* or *"How do we handle disciplinary appeals?"*
- System automatically detects document type for better retrieval
- Every answer includes specific references to your uploaded documents (no hallucinations)
- Search in English or Bahasa Indonesia

**Key Capability:** Retrieval Augmented Generation (RAG)
- Multi-document context aggregation
- Semantic chunking for precise retrieval
- Document-grounded response generation

**Use Case Example:**
> Principal uploads the new student handbook. A teacher asks: *"Can parents appeal a suspension?"* The system retrieves relevant sections, provides exact procedures, cites document references, and includes timeline requirements—all in 10 seconds.

---

### 3. Conversational Intent Recognition

No command syntax to memorize. Just speak naturally:

| Natural Language Input | System Action | Result |
|---|---|---|
| *"Can you evaluate my students' essays?"* | Initiates grading workflow | Upload essays → Get grades & feedback |
| *"Add this PDF to my knowledge base"* | Document upload preparation | Auto-classify & index documents |
| *"What's the attendance policy?"* | Knowledge base search | Retrieve policy with direct citations |
| *"Schedule a staff meeting tomorrow at 3 PM"* | Calendar management | Event created with reminder |
| *"How many credits do I have left?"* | Account check | Balance displayed instantly |
| *"Switch to Bahasa Indonesia"* | Language toggle | Interface language changed |

